title: My main menu button. Won't swipe up and won't let me off any open apps. What can I do?
content:
Button won't swipe up or let me come out of apps or swipe up to the menu. Ive Googled it and it said to download Nova launcher which I did. It worked for a short while. But now nothing. I've reset the phone. I've put the assessabilty button on to help but that won't open either. None of the buttons at the very bottom of the phone work. 
I have a Google pixel 3.
